INSERT INTO `bsi_hotels` VALUES (1,'Testing - Holiday Inn Golden Mile','50 Nathan Road, ','Tsim Sha Tsui, Hong Kong','Tsim Sha Tsui','.','.','2','marcohung@gmail.com','21453322','','','<p>Holiday Inn Golden Mile offers convenience with Tsimshatsui MTR subway station at its doorstep. It features 4 dining options and a rooftop pool. Free WiFi is also available throughout the hotel. Free smartphones will be offered as well for staying guests to make calls and use 3G and WiFi access.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In Kowloon&#39;s city center, Holiday Inn Golden Mile Hong Kong is a 40-minute drive from Hong Kong International Airport. It is .4.8 km from Ocean Terminal and a 5-minute walk from Star Ferry Terminal and the Victoria Harbourfront.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Rooms at Holiday Inn Golden Mile are fitted with classic wood furnishings and calming pastel shades. In-room conveniences include an LCD TV with cable channels, iPod docking station and a safe.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Refreshing workouts await at the well-equipped fitness center. After a day of activity, enjoy soothing massages and the use of sauna facilities. Childcare services and a 24-hour business center are available.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Fine Cantonese dishes can be sampled at Loong Yuen while Bistro on the Mile offers hearty international buffet spreads. With live music, Hari&rsquo;s Bar is ideal for an after-meal cocktail. Osteria Ristorante Italiano is on Mezzanine Floor with traditional Italian specialties.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tsim Sha Tsui is a great choice for travelers interested in&nbsp;luxury-brand shopping,clothes shopping&nbsp;and&nbsp;disneyland.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In this area you can shop &#39;til you drop for popular brands like Rolex, Cartier, Gucci, Tiffany &amp; Co, Louis Vuitton.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We speak your language!</p>\r\n','','',0,'22.297018','114.172641','<p>All children are welcome.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Free!</strong>&nbsp;Up to two children under 18 years stay free of charge when using existing beds.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>One older child or adult is charged HKD 450 per person per night in an extra bed.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The maximum number of extra beds/cribs in a room is 1.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Any type of extra bed or crib is upon request and needs to be confirmed by management.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Additional fees are not calculated automatically in the total cost and will have to be paid for separately during your stay.</p>\r\n',1,'202cb962ac59075b964b07152d234b70',5,'1447814956_13587820.jpg','<p>An American breakfast buffet is served at the open-air Cen Caf&eacute;, which also offers local and international dishes. Thai specialities can be enjoyed on the beach at Le Bassye&#39; Coffee-Shop &amp; Restauran</p>\r\n',''),(2,'eLog Inn (A Day Hotel)','Flat G, 8/F, Lucky House, 22 Jordan Road, Yau Ma Tei, Hong Kong, Hong Kong','','Causeway Bay','Jordan','.','1','heihei1983@live.hk','94857653','','','<p>There is ticket service at the property.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Temple Street Night Market&nbsp;is 300 m from eLog Inn (A Day Hotel), and Kowloon Park is 501 m from the property. Hong Kong International Airport is 24.1 km away.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Yau Ma Tei is a great choice for travelers interested in&nbsp;disneyland,&nbsp;gourmet food&nbsp;andshopping.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In this area you can shop &#39;til you drop for popular brands like Rolex, Cartier, Gucci, Tiffany &amp; Co, Louis Vuitton.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We speak your language!</p>\r\n','','',0,'22.30501','114.1708555','<p>Cancellation and prepayment policies vary according to room type. Please&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.booking.com/hotel/hk/elog-inn.html#availability_target\">enter the dates of your stay</a>&nbsp;and check what conditions apply to your preferred room.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>å–æ¶ˆæ”¿ç­–</p>\r\n',1,'202cb962ac59075b964b07152d234b70',3,'1447814708_55176069.jpg','',''),(4,'Testing W Hong Kong Hotel ','1 Austin Road West, Kowloon Station, Kowloon, Tsim Sha Tsui, Hong Kong','','Tsim Sha Tsui','','0','2','w@whotel.com','28475930','','','<p>Located near Airport Express, guests can get immersed in the artistic ambience of West Kowloon Culture Center. The hotel features 393 rooms with skyline views, all rooms are equipped with modern facilities for your comfort. The property showcase glamorous trends blending in with a colonial style that will delight you. For dining options, try Sing Yin Cantonese Dining, the dazzling KITCHEN, and the chic WOOBAR. Guests can enjoy themselves at the rooftop WET pool, chill out at Asia&rsquo;s first Bliss Spa, or work out among the clouds at FIT. For every other wish, the hotel&rsquo;s Whatever/Whenever service is at your command. If you&rsquo;re looking for a special and unique experience, look no further than W Hong Kong Hotel.</p>\r\n','','',0,'22.304953','114.160478','<p>tttttccccc</p>\r\n',1,'202cb962ac59075b964b07152d234b70',5,'1448873410_200056_15060810550028823972.jpg','<ul>\r\n	<li>Guests over 12 years old are considered as adults.</li>\r\n	<li>Extra beds are dependent on the room you choose, please check the individual room policy for more details.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n','<p>Parking Fee (per day)500 HKD</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Room Voltage220</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Time to Airport (Minutes)30</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Year Hotel Built2008</p>\r\n');
